INSTALLATION
# 1. Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/lewis-karani/Advanced-Bioinformatics-Training

# 2. change to the dir
cd sarscov2/

# 3. download and install all the packages you need 
conda env create -f environment_file.yml

# 4. acviate the conda environment with all the packages
conda activate sarscov2
create an environment named sarscov2 by running the following commands using the yaml file provided ie. environment_file.yml

```
conda env create --file environment_file.yml

```

